dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:100,000 scale maps of Papua, Indonesia, titled 'Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Seibu Papua jūmanbun no ichi -- Seibu Papua jūmanbun no ichi -- 空中寫真測圖要圖西部パプア十万分一 -- 西部パプア十万分一/Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Seibu Papua jūmanbun no ichi.' To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
